snippet.title: LIVE FOOTAGE* Amber Heard Confronts Johnny Depp Supporter For Mean Tweet!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard over the last few years has been singing a very specific narrative in terms of her viewpoint on ex-husband and as he started to prove that not everything Amber Heard said was true, he started to turn people to his side. So much so that there has been a public outcry for Amber Heard to go and be removed from certain roles that she's in. But, while they have been loud, Amber Heard has been just as loud at bashing them. Allow us to show you what we mean. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!
